title: BEST OF: #030: Jim Jefferies
itunes:title: BEST OF: #030: Jim Jefferies
description: Adam and Drew sit down with comic Jim Jefferies, star of FX's Legit, to discuss why its harder to sell tickets in Los Angeles as well as the infuriating differences between today and the Elvis/Sinatra era.  Later they discuss how tuned out people have become and examine some comments made about Adam by another radio host.
